data.meta_description: Download this stock image: Dutch Prime Minister Jan Peter Balkenende reacts when visiting a green house in Ter Aar, some 35 kilometers from Amsterdam, Netherlands, Monday Nov. 20, 2006. Balkenende is on a campaign trail for upcoming Nov. 22 elections. The green house is heated with natural warm water, not using any natural gas and has zero CO2 emissions. (AP Photo/Peter Dejong) - 2PCA4FY from Alamy's library of millions of high resolution stock photos, illustrations and vectors.
